title: Quake Deathmatch maker v1.0
description:
Deathmatch Maker, The First Quake Level Editor Authorized By id Software.

What more is it to say really? 

It was one of the first levelcreators for Quake that i heard of. I created a couple of funfilled levels with this one :)
Anyway, i guess people have moved on to better editors by now. This is purely for the nostalgic feeling. I found it the back of my closet so i thought it needed some replay value.

Have fun:D
